{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban people posting images of nude or partially undressed children online",
        "additional_details": "As a mum of two, I want to speak up for children as they are unable to consent to this content and this content can allow for online predators and/or paedophiles to have access. I think it is a significant online safety risk. I am particularly concerned about influencers and content creators with large online followings.",
        "background": "I want to introduce a ban on people posting images or videos of their children or other children without clothes, such as in their nappy or exposed swimwear.",
